ion and random scattering. We discover that the different dendrites'\narchitectures are associated with different Laplace and diffusion fields, which\ngovern the monomers trajectory and subsequent dendrites' growth. Such\nunconventional engineering routes could have a variety of applications from\nneuromorphic engineering to bottom-up computing strategies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jul 2021 17:35:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-08"}
