y Loss. These results can be used in future research to extract\nmore geometric information from the segmentation masks or could even be\nimplemented on other types of fire accidents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jul 2021 19:52:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Aug 2021 21:13:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 1 Nov 2021 23:22:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-21"}
