 for iterated function systems with\nplace-dependent probabilities (place-dependent Bernoulli convolutions and the\nBlackwell measure for binary channel) and equilibrium measures for hyperbolic\nIFS with overlaps (in particular: natural measures for non-homogeneous\nself-similar IFS and certain systems corresponding to random continued\nfractions).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Jul 2021 09:12:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 29 Jan 2022 19:59:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Feb 2022 18:46:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-04"}
