, all\nbut one were found to be late-types. 21 have EWs consistent with those of RSGs,\n16 with those of O-rich Mira AGBs, and one with an S-type AGB. These infrared\nresults open new, unexplored, potential for searches at low-resolution of RSGs\nin the highly obscured innermost regions of the Milky Way.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Jul 2021 09:32:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-20"}
