 These results are particularized\nfor the so-called Rayleigh dissipation, that is, external forces that can be\nwritten as the derivative of a \"potential\" with respect to the velocities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Jul 2021 11:43:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-12"}
